meta.about: Responsible Packaging Connecting A Sustainable Community. #INVISIBLEBAG is water-soluble, compostable and biodegradable. No conventional PP, PE, PS, PVC Plastics, non-toxic and leaves no harmful residues behind. An alternative for brands to replace conventional plastic packaging, and now consumers have a choice to just dissolve it in hot water!
